ZH: 这篇文章内容太空泛了。
EN: The content of this article is too superficial.

ZH: 他的想法太空泛，缺乏具体的细节。
EN: His ideas are too vague, lacking specific details.

ZH: 忽略了这个问题的重要细节，只做了一些空泛的讨论。
EN: Ignoring the important details of this issue, only a superficial discussion was made.

ZH: 这个计划的目标太过空泛，缺乏可行性。
EN: The goals of this plan are too vague and lack feasibility.

ZH: 这个报告太空泛了，没有明确的建议。
EN: This report is too superficial, with no specific recommendations.

ZH: 对于这个复杂的问题，我们不能只用空泛的说法来掩盖事实。
EN: For this complex issue, we cannot just use superficial words to cover up the facts.

ZH: 这个理论过于空泛，无法应用于实际问题。
EN: This theory is too superficial to be applied to practical problems.

ZH: 这份研究结果太过空泛，缺乏深入分析。
EN: The findings of this study are too superficial, lacking in-depth analysis.

ZH: 他的演讲内容太空泛，没有引起观众的兴趣。
EN: His speech was too superficial, failing to capture the audience's interest.

ZH: 他的批评内容太空泛，缺乏具体例证。
EN: His criticisms were too superficial, lacking concrete examples.

ZH: 我们需要避免在讨论重要问题时陷入空泛的陈述。
EN: We need to avoid falling into superficial statements when discussing important issues.

ZH: 这篇文章只是涉及表面问题，没有深挖核心问题。
EN: This article only touches on surface issues, without delving into the core problems.

ZH: 这个计划的目标太过空泛，需要进一步明确细节。
EN: The goals of this plan are too vague and need further clarification of details.

ZH: 他的演讲内容过于空泛，没有深入探讨实质问题。
EN: His speech was too superficial, lacking in-depth discussion of substantive issues.

ZH: 这份报告提出的方案很空泛，没有具体实施计划。
EN: The proposals in this report are very superficial, without specific implementation plans.

ZH: 我们不能只停留在空泛的宏观理论上，需要着眼于具体问题。
EN: We cannot just stay at the superficial macro theory level and need to focus on specific issues.

ZH: 他的批评内容太空泛，没有深入分析原因。
EN: His criticisms were too superficial, lacking in-depth analysis of the reasons.

ZH: 关于这个问题的讨论太过空泛，需要更深入的探究。
EN: The discussion of this issue is too superficial and requires more in-depth exploration.

ZH: 这项计划的目标需要更具体明确，避免过于抽象空泛。
EN: The goals of this plan need to be more specific and clear to avoid being too abstract and superficial.

ZH: 他的研究成果只是一些空泛的描述，缺乏实质性内容。
EN: His research findings are just some superficial descriptions, lacking substantive content.
